
  Anorith    Rock Type Pokémon

  ANORITH was regenerated from 
  a prehistoric fossil.  This primitive 
  Pokémon once lived in warm seas. 
   It grips its prey firmly between 
  its two large claws. 
	Evolution Chain
      Anorith ► Armaldo

